  <name>VLDB-Toolkits</name>
  <summary>Paper Management Platform for Academic Research</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      VLDB-Toolkits is a comprehensive desktop application designed for managing academic papers
      and author information. It provides powerful tools for researchers, academics, and conference
      organizers to efficiently handle large datasets of research papers.
    </p>
    <p>Key Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Import and export Excel data with ease</li>
      <li>Track paper metadata including titles, authors, abstracts, and keywords</li>
      <li>Manage author profiles with affiliations and contact information</li>
      <li>Advanced search and filtering capabilities</li>
      <li>Export organized datasets in multiple formats</li>
      <li>Clean and intuitive user interface</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

